After allo-HCT, patients can experience a number of different events. The appropriate statistical framework is a competing risks model48, which allows one to estimate the probability of occurrence of each event (by accounting for the possibility of the others occurring). Assuming that K different events can occur, we define \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
